SAM STEINBERG and JOSEPH N. SMITH v. DR. EMIL ALTER, MORRIS MARGOLIS and SAM PELSMAN. 20 So. (2nd) 911

January Term, 1915

February 16, 1945 Division A Henry D. Williams, and Morris' S. Salomon, for appellants. Redfearn & Ferrell and Leo Rosen, for appellees. *573PER CURIAM:

The decree appealed from is affirmed on authority of out opinion in Rundel v. Gordon, et al., 92 Fla. 1110, 111 So. 386.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur. 1
